messageBody:
> http://slate.langan.net/readunicode/

That's a mighty nice font you have there.
Have you made it available anywhere?

Hi Benct,

The font I used as the basis for the unicode tests is "Jeremy."  It was created by a group member and should be in the files section of the Read_Alphabet group.  It is meant to be a printed (i.e., "Junior") font, and was based on New Century Schoolbook.

oliver
